children.text: importjava.util.*;publicclassL2{publicstaticvoidmain(String[]args){Scannersc=newScanner(System.in);System.out.print("Enter weight in pounds: ");doubleberat=sc.nextDouble();System.out.print("Enter feet: ");doublefeet=sc.nextDouble();System.out.print("Enter inches: ");doubleinci=sc.nextDouble();doubletinggi=feet*12+inci;doublebmi=berat*0.45359237/((tinggi*0.0254)*(tinggi*0.0254));System.out.println("BMI is "+bmi);if(bmi<18.5){System.out.println("Underweight");}elseif(bmi<25){System.out.println("Normal");}elseif(bmi<30){System.out.println("Overweight");}else{System.out.println("Obese");}}}
